# Cascade Workspace AI Rules

This workspace is governed by the following Cascade memories:

1. Core AI Behavior Guidelines
   - Prevents unwanted improvements and suggestions
   - Controls when changes can be proposed
   - Prohibits lazy loading suggestions

2. Required Technology Stack
   - Enforces consistent technology choices
   - Prevents introduction of alternative libraries
   - Maintains framework consistency

3. CBP Model Synchronization Rule
   - Protects infrastructure models
   - Ensures alignment with legacy system
   - Prevents feature creep in infrastructure

4. CBP Service Layer Integration Rules
   - Maintains service factory pattern
   - Prevents alternate API implementation patterns
   - Ensures consistent service layer usage
